cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CR 

This paper deals with deep learning and imbalanced data problems, which are common issues in computer vision, machine learning, and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper also discusses the use of deep neural networks, which falls under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper proposes a method to improve the performance of deep learning models, which could be relevant to the sub-category cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
